snippet.title: Witch It 1.0 Launch Trailer
snippet.description:
Witch It 1.0 is Available Now!
https://store.steampowered.com/app/559650/Witch_It/
Witch It is a multiplayer hide & seek game.
Hunters are tasked with seeking hidden witches that blend in with the environment - trust no furnishing, grocery, or utensil!

You are a Content Creator and need a Steam-Key!?
Apply here: https://dodistribute.com/access/LtLoWqheXz/

Witch It Twitter:https://twitter.com/WitchItGame
   DEV    Twitter:https://twitter.com/Barrelrolldev

Music by: Jan-Helge Schnöbbe
http://www.jhsoundtracks.de/
